# WML and Lua File Conventions

- Keep examples syntactically valid for `1.19.x`.
- Write generated pipeline files under `docs/wesnoth/generated/`.
- Add version requirements to new examples:
  - WML files: `# Requires: 1.19.X+`
  - Lua files: `-- Requires: 1.19.X+`
- Prefer explicit migration-safe edits over broad refactors.
- When replacing deprecated patterns, include the modern equivalent in comments or notes.
